    public static final class EkmServiceGrpc.EkmServiceStub
extends io.grpc.stub.AbstractAsyncStub<EkmServiceGrpc.EkmServiceStub>
    A stub to allow clients to do asynchronous rpc calls to service EkmService. 
     Google Cloud Key Management EKM Service
 Manages external cryptographic keys and operations using those keys.
 Implements a REST model with the following objects:
 * [EkmConnection][google.cloud.kms.v1.EkmConnection]

      • verifyConnectivity

        public void verifyConnectivity​(VerifyConnectivityRequest request,
                               io.grpc.stub.StreamObserver<VerifyConnectivityResponse> responseObserver)
         Verifies that Cloud KMS can successfully connect to the external key
 manager specified by an [EkmConnection][google.cloud.kms.v1.EkmConnection].
 If there is an error connecting to the EKM, this method returns a
 FAILED_PRECONDITION status containing structured information as described
 at https://cloud.google.com/kms/docs/reference/ekm_errors.
